title: Match History - Blank?
body:
Hey guys, I have played a few games in the last fortnight and went to have a look at some stats etc and upon checking my match history nothing is showing up? Tried on mobile, my account, friends account another computer, and still nothing. Any Ideas?
Kind Regards, {{champion:254}}  Blacky.

replies.body: In client or on the web? The web match history does have an issue atm, and they're working on a fix so it should be back soon. In the mean time the in-client match history should work fine.
